title: Allan Quatermain and the Lost City of Gold
description:
Genre: Action & Adventure

Year: 1987

Director: Gary Nelson

Cast: Richard Chamberlain, Sharon Stone, James Earl Jones, Henry Silva, Robert Donner, Doghmi Larbi, Aileen Marson, Cassandra Peterson, Martin Rabbett, Rory Kilalea, Alex Heyns, Themsi Times, Philip Boucher, Stuart Goakes, Fidelis Cheza.

Synopsis: After his brother Robeson disappears without a trace while exploring Africa in search of a legendary &#039;white tribe&#039;(King Solomon&#039;s Mines), Alan Quatermain decides to follow in his footsteps to learn what became of him. Soon after arriving, he discovers the los City of Gold, controlled by the evil lord Agon, and mined by his legions of white slaves. Is this where Robeson met his end?
